#######################################################################################

This script assumes that you already have sudo configured for the user wich executes it

Please, download moodle.sh to your machine and make it executable 
Do sh moodle.sh 

Login to your Moodle server by your browser with user moodle and password Vmware!1
Don't forget to change this password! 


